  "commentary": {
    "neutral_announcer_espn": "This is a classic kitchen battle, with both players demonstrating excellent touch and control. The rally goes on for quite some time, showcasing their patience and ability to reset the ball. Unfortunately for the player on the left, the streak ends with a net cord error.",
